{
  "stem": "1413.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They-- the Germans-- when I was in a small town, they send us-- the German sought whoever, no, the Americans they did transportation.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They bought us to Ulm.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "U-L-M.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In this place of Ulm.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "From there-- they-- we were a day or two, maybe the same day-- they sent us on the Autobahn to Mannheim.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And from Mannheim, I was put in a train to the Netherlands.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went to Eindhoven. 12 It's in the south of the Netherlands, because we couldn't go the bridge on account of there was no bridge.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was bombed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a movie made from that, and the guy who made it was a Dutch fellow by the name of-- well, it's immaterial.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anyway, that was-- and-- they gave us sleeping arrangement in Eindhoven, in the well-known company, Phillips.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Phillips makes all electrical things-- you name it-- one of the biggest in the world.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And from there, they were sent to private homes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the name of the place, the small town near Eindhoven, the name of this place was Geldrop.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "G-E-L-D-R-O-P.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- maybe a week or so till my brother-in-law who worked for the underground, as I told you before, Gentile, came and brought me back to Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Through the Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I moved in with my sister-in-law.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If I may say so, for posterity, for the future to know, that when I came back one Saturday night, we got to know that my sister-in-law's-- my in-law parents came back from wherever they were, I think Theresienstadt, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they had to be picked up from the train station-- Central station-- I've got a picture that had been hanging there of that station.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had to pick them up to come back also from Germany.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
